==English==
===Noun phrase===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[w:Coulomb|Coulomb]] [[explosion]]'''
#{{physics}} the effect of a [[molecule]] moving at high speed [[striking]] a [[solid]]; [[binding]] [[electron]]s being [[torn]] off, and the resulting [[charged]] [[constituent]]s [[separating]] due to [[Coulomb repulsion]]
